                        <h3 class="help_h3">Tourist Tube Page</h3>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title">This page shows all your activities on Tourist Tube as well as actions of other Tubers on your activities. It can be made accessible in full or in part to selected users according to the privacy settings you set. This page shows the following elements:</p>
                        <ul class="main_ul_list_help">
