                                    <li>others’ entries</li>
                                    <li>hotels</li>
                                    <li>restaurants</li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>A list of my Friends<li>
                            <li>A list of people following me<li>
                            <li>A list of people I am following<li>
                            <li>A list of my Events (both those I created and those I joined)<li>
                            <li>A list of my Channels<li>
                            <li>A list of Channels I am following<li>
                            <li>A list of my Channels’ Events<li>
                            <li>Suggested Channels<li>
