                            <li>Tourist Tuber Notifications-showing only you and according to settings you chose return actions-related to your activities<li>
                        </ul>
                        <h3 class="help_h3">Account Info</h3>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title"><span class="underline">Personal Info:</span> You can edit your personal info including given names, gender, date of birth, address, picture, web address, comments, educational background, occupation, interests, etc.</p>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title"><span class="underline">Settings:</span> You can edit your Tourist Tube account settings including user name and password. You can also deactivate your account temporarily or delete it permanently. You can also choose to stop receiving emails from Tourist Tube.</p>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title"><span class="underline">Activities:</span> You can see a summary and history of your account activities, including joining date, number of friends, number of uploaded photos, videos,albums, journals and events as well as number of likes and comments received, and statistics on your network followings</p>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title"><span class="underline">Notifications :</span> Add your email address to receive email notifications of your Tourist Tube account activities. You can choose to receive notifications by email and/or on your Tourist Tube page. As an example, Tourist Tube will automatically send you notifications for each of the checked events below:</p>
                        <ul class="main_ul_list_help">
                            <li>One of my uploads receives comments or likes<li> 
                            <li>I receive a friend invitation from another Tuber<li> 
                            <li>Someone added me as a friend<li> 
                            <li>Someone follows me<li> 
                            <li>Someone replies to my comment<li> 
                        </ul>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title"><span class="underline">Invitations :</span> You can send up to 50 invitations to join Tourist Tube just by filling the names and emails of your friends and acquaintances</p>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title"><span class="underline">Sharing :</span> If you wish to share your Tourist Tube posts with your other social networking platforms, you can easily set up a connection between Tourist Tube and your selected platforms, including Facebook, Google+, Twitter and Yahoo. </p>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title"><span class="underline">Privacy Settings :</span> Tourist Tube assigns permissions to people contacting you and to people acting on your activities. </p>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title"><span class="underline">Contact privacy:</span> Who can look me up? </p>
