                        <h3 class="help_h3">Friends</h3>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title">You can search for, see all your friends on Tourist Tube, and get in contact with them. Tubers with similar interests are also suggested for you to contact.</p>
                        <h3 class="help_h3">News Feeds</h3>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title">This page shows you only activities of Tourist Tube users you are interested in according to the privacy settings they set. These users can be: </p>
                        <ul class="main_ul_list_help">
