                        <h3 class="help_h3">Events</h3>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title">This is an organizer to create, edit and publish your events. You can set your event viewing privacy; you can also show your event’s guests list, allow your guests to invite others and enable shares and comments on the event. </p>
                        <h3 class="help_h3">Journals</h3>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title">This is an organizer to create, edit and publish your journals. Journals can contain photos and text comments or entries. Journals can be published online to pdf format. You can add word and place tags to your journals upon publishing to improve Search Engines visibility.  </p>
                        <h3 class="help_h3">Favorites</h3>
                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title">This is an organizer to find and save your favorite TT photos, videos, albums, and journals </p>
