                        <p class="faq_sub_header_title"><span class="underline">Channel Setup:</span> You can setup a channel as a new user or as a regular user. Regular users can set up as many channels as they wish. If you wish to use for your channel an email already associated with an existing account, you are given the opportunity to claim this email for your channel. All created channels are public</p>
